_xResult.title: A Dare Bodysuit
_xResult.shortdesc: Custom made lace bodysuit with baby doll sleeves
_xResult.longdesc:
Being daring is never easy. It is never the safe one’s who are called out, but the daring ones that make the difference. Don’t let them think any differently in this made to measure Chantilly bodysuit. Wear this as a mysterious alternative to blouses or pair it with an elegant skirt to make for a daring evening outfit.

You need a top made custom to your measurements. You'll love the feeling of knowing it's made just for you and fits you perfectly!
